{"tid":2490885,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"呈新片力陳遭警叉頸 未能推翻襲警罪  被告拍掌讚官 陳慶偉：可當藐視","createTime":"2021-04-16T02:40:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T04:36:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"315c2d54ee45ce60d6f76fcf596a60ee78c2313e","tid":2490885,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T02:40:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210416/ADIIRG35PRHMTB6N4P5JA53JTA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210416%2FADIIRG35PRHMTB6N4P5JA53JTA%2F&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwLPkHgDHOcRHwLuXI7BMvHI%3D&h=c75ba20e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210416%2FADIIRG35PRHMTB6N4P5JA53JTA%2F&h=d093ebd6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210416/ADIIRG35PRHMTB6N4P5JA53JTA/</a><br />\n<br />\n呈新片力陳遭警叉頸 未能推翻襲警罪 <br />\n被告拍掌讚官 陳慶偉：可當藐視<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/t83rOm9nHtQEifoDWbxih5h1rKk=/510x253/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QOFGUO4VEFE4RJNLQW2EJPERAE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Ft83rOm9nHtQEifoDWbxih5h1rKk%3D%2F510x253%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQOFGUO4VEFE4RJNLQW2EJPERAE.jpg&h=137f1474&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n手機用戶請按此放大圖表<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】六旬司機去年1月在中環「天下制裁」集會現場附近，被指襲擊速龍警員，遭多名警員制服拘捕，頭破血流，同年8月被裁定襲警罪成，判監一個月。司機不服定罪和判刑，找來新證據片段向高等法院提出上訴，力陳非但沒有襲警，反而遭警員叉頸。法官陳慶偉昨指片段內容無助推翻定罪，不接納他遭叉頸才自衞還擊的說法，駁回上訴，司機庭上拍掌向法官稱：「我讚美你！」惟惹來陳官不滿，警告司機「你剛才嘅舉動可以構成藐視法庭」。法官最終凝視司機良久後宣佈休庭。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/6i5-F_t4ViiCFGxlJz1IPaxnoTw=/510x340/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YW4AFFRRPZBSZLO6SSO7CR5TM4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F6i5-F_t4ViiCFGxlJz1IPaxnoTw%3D%2F510x340%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYW4AFFRRPZBSZLO6SSO7CR5TM4.jpg&h=8ade6e25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■被指襲警的上訴人施振英，被捕當日頭破血流。<br />\n<br />\n法官陳慶偉庭上宣佈上訴結果，指考慮過雙方陳詞及上訴理據、最重要是新提交的案發當日拍攝片段後，認為無論定罪或刑期上訴均理據不足。犯人欄內的上訴人施振英（61歲）聞判即大力拍掌六下，並向陳官豎起拇指。陳官沉默兩秒後問施是何用意，施回應「我讚美你」，但陳官質疑「似乎你唔係好滿意個結果」，施否認，更稱：「全香港市民都滿意你！」惟陳官沉默良久表示施的舉動可構成藐視法庭。最終律師以手勢示意施冷靜，施再沒答話，陳官才宣佈休庭。<br />\n<br />\n施被帶入囚室前，旁聽人士大叫：「施生，頂住呀！」施則叮囑兒子謂：「睇住你媽咪呀！」施的兒子在庭外稱，上訴聆訊時「睇到個官咁態度，都冇乜寄望」，只是家人和父親仍心存希望，最終希望落空。<br />\n<br />\n陳官在判詞中指，上訴方新增證據片段與審訊呈堂影片內容大致脗合，分別只在拍攝角度不同，但相關片段其實早已存在，亦知來源，不難找到，直指上訴方沒有盡力尋找，無法解釋為何在原審時提交不到。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n判詞指上訴方雞蛋裏挑骨頭<br />\n<br />\n上訴方指稱遭警員叉頸才自。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n判詞續指，上訴方將證供上。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n刑罰方面，判詞指施當日在馬。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：HCMA250/20"},{"pid":"e7181f4fbff5a93797bac056c191491b2e07ae9c","tid":2490885,"uid":292987,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T02:48:55.000Z","msg":"狗官 又要奶又怕俾人唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e83b8290bbe0486fb302dd913ca51905ccd8b4a0","tid":2490885,"uid":3241,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T02:49:58.000Z","msg":"差句感謝共產党法官"},{"pid":"d58888db89eac21c5d016c5fe085c816dacd4395","tid":2490885,"uid":282637,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T02:57:33.000Z","msg":"笑得唔岩佢心水都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0f4bfd2cde2d4c11eb56ff4370cf380c069c6c9","tid":2490885,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T02:59:19.000Z","msg":"趁地淋啦依啲仆街"},{"pid":"876601787a3789100de4c43b28c8a1aa4a29f8f9","tid":2490885,"uid":53673,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T03:05:01.000Z","msg":"好似拍咗六下<br />\n係咪代表DLLMCH？"},{"pid":"b25c16149bce452318967d5e6589720309a5a2c1","tid":2490885,"uid":113498,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0